 <PERSON> Ed </PERSON> <PERSON> Blanche </PERSON>, the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION>'s <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> East </LOCATION> news editor based in <LOCATION> Nicosia </LOCATION>, covered the Iranian revolution in 1979 and has written on <LOCATION> Iranian </LOCATION> affairs since 1985.
